step-0: download llama2 model and copy it in models folder (this link is recommended for local use https://huggingface.co/TheBloke/Llama-2-7B-Chat-GGML/blob/main/llama-2-7b-chat.ggmlv3.q8_0.bin)
Step-1: in your cmd create a conda environment ,exemple command:
    conda create -p llmenv python==3.9           
step-2: activate the conda environment:
    conda activate <Path to Folder>
step-3: cd to the folder where you cloned the project
step-4: run in cmd
     pip install -r requirements.txt
step-5: run in cmd
     streamlit run app.py
